<b>"Strength and Honor"<b></font><P><i><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/uwildviene.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wildviene</A> at: 5/1/01 10:04:39 pm</FONT><br></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/uwordaensilvershadow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wordaen Silvershadow</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Buff God</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>251</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF33>5/2/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF33>11:25:15 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.bellsnwhistles.com/afla/afi020.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif">&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Raid Conduct</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well,<br>
<br>
Please don't take this wrong all, but I am afraid I have to agree with Wild on this one. Yes, we have a responsibility as Elites to behave in a manner other than what was given to us. Yes, we hold ourselves to a higher standard. <br>
<br>
