<br>
Like Wild said, it is easy to get this NPC to pop. THe trick is to get to her BEFORE someone else on that floor DOES. This is common, it happens all the time. This guy that verbally hassled me should have opened up his mouth when we RAN BY him and said something like &quot;/ooc Killin PH for Cara, pls let me grab her&quot;. He didn't. There were 20+ ppl in zone when we were there, I looked. And quite frankly, if someone does not call that, then others WILL consider the spawn open. I equate this to someone going off on me for not even being in zone and yelling obscenities at me if I see the AC in S Ro and kill it. Oh wait, they were timing it. Too bad, it was not called.<br>
